publisher			Flyleap Studios							
publish_time	 2016年5月23日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Experience the rush of FPV racing and even develop real life drone flight skills with the life-like physics found in this sim. If you already have drone racing experience, this sim supports many Radio Controllers and will enable you do develop skills on new challenging courses. If you're just starting out, the game also supports gamepads, joysticks and keyboard and mouse (playing with keyboard not recommended).Key FeaturesPainless MultiplayerSupports real Radio ControllersLife-like PhysicsSkill Testing/High ChallengePretty LookingThe game features what is perhaps the most painless and functional multiplayer of any other drone sim, with the ability to easily join into multiplayer races at the click of a button. With some custom netcode, the game should never feel laggy to play and enable people to compete all around the world in the same environment. Racing multicopters is much harder than it looks on youtube, if nothing else this sim will help you develop appreciation for the skill involved in what looks like simple manouvers. Prepare to test your patience on the game's highly challenging courses.						
